DESCRIPTION
-----------

REQUIREMENTS
------------
This is an iOS app, made for iPhones and iPads. It is only available via the Apple App Store, and requires iOS 5.0 or above.

INSTALLATION
------------

This will be installed via the Apple App Store, and will be a free app.

